msgstr "Tip"

#. module: account_reconcile_sale_order
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:account_reconcile_sale_order.field_account_reconcile_model__sale_order_matching_token_match
msgid ""
"When this is activated, the statement line's label is split into words and "
"if one of those words match a sales order, it is considered a match. So if "
"the statement line's label is 'hello world', sales orders with names "
"'hello', 'world', 'some name containing hello', 'some name containing world'"
" will be considered matches, in that order"
msgstr ""
"Ko je ta možnost aktivirana, se oznaka postavke izpiska razčleni na besede, "
"in če se katera od teh besed ujema s prodajnim nalogom, se to šteje za "
"ujemanje. Če je torej oznaka vrstice izpiska 'hello world', se bodo prodajni "
"nalogi z imeni 'hello', 'world', 'kakšno ime, ki vsebuje besedo hello' in "
"'kakšno ime, ki vsebuje besedo world' šteli za ujemanja, in sicer v tem "
"vrstnem redu"
